00:01:14.380 --> 00:01:20.800
So I want to talk a bit
about the history of Apollo 8

00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:25.510
and the historical
significance of Apollo 8.

00:01:25.510 --> 00:01:30.230
And I hope you'll forgive me
if I glance down quite a bit

00:01:30.230 --> 00:01:32.950
and do as much
reading as speaking.

00:01:32.950 --> 00:01:38.050
Extemporaneously, I am
a shameless wind bag,

00:01:38.050 --> 00:01:39.610
so when I write
things down, they

00:01:39.610 --> 00:01:42.070
